book("The Hour of Magic (Geronimo Stilton and the Kingdom of Fantasy #8)", ["Geronimo Stilton"], "Scholastic Inc.", "2016-05-31", "Fairies, dragons, wizards, and more await Geronimo on every magical Kingdom of Fantasy adventure! I, Geronimo Stilton, was amazed to find myself called back to the Kingdom of Fantasy for another adventure. Blossom, Queen of the Fairies, needed my help -- time itself was under threat! Something evil was making the hands of the magical Tick Tock Timepiece spin faster and faster. It was causing Blossom to age at an alarming rate . . . and if she perished, so would the entire Kingdom of Fantasy! Holey cheese! It was up to me to restore time and harmony to the land. Could I do it before the clock reached its final hour?", "0545826187", "9780545826181", 324, ["Juvenile Fiction"], "en", "http://books.google.com/books/content?id=qzPRCgAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api", 5, 2, "http://books.google.co.th/books?id=qzPRCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA312&dq=fantasy&hl=&cd=32&source=gbs_api", "https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=qzPRCgAAQBAJ&source=gbs_api").
