book("Entrepreneurship", ["Álvaro Cuervo", "Domingo Ribeiro", "Salvador Roig"], "Springer Science & Business Media", "2007-05-26", "Entrepreneurship can, at times, seem like a veritable jungle where finding one's way can prove to be difficult. This book functions as a map locating the most important issues: those where an acceptable consensus already exists, and those that remain open to discussion. In so doing, we have presented the accounts of distinguished explorers in their own words.", "3540485430", "9783540485438", 348, ["Business & Economics"], "en", "http://books.google.com/books/content?id=2v-aWpdgoPQC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api", 5, 1, "http://books.google.co.th/books?id=2v-aWpdgoPQC&pg=PA132&dq=Entrepreneurship&hl=&cd=1&source=gbs_api", "https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=2v-aWpdgoPQC&source=gbs_api").
